Introduction

Jinny is a Korean-American singer. She is a former member of the girl group SECRET NUMBER and made her official debut with the group on May 19, 2020, with the single album "Who Dis?".

Originally a trainee under YG Entertainment, Jinny was a pre-debut member of BLACKPINK, but was cut from the final lineup. After five years, she left the company sometime in 2018. Later that year, she participated in the Mnet survival show "Produce 48" as an independent trainee and was eliminated on episode 5 after ranking in 69th place.

On April 4, 2025, she, alongside members Dita and Minji, released a collective statement announcing their departures from the group as well as Vine Entertainment.
